inbodydescription.para: < We want to remove one body to make it the final destination, but we also want at least one other destination.
< We want the final body to be Kerbin about half of the time for randoms, and all the time for focused tours.
< A body and a moon is not a tour.
< Before we try to offer a tour, we want to know the player has been to all these places in single missions first.
